dcterms:description: The UFPR-ALPR dataset is used to evaluate the performance of automatic license plate recognition systems under various challenging conditions, including lighting changes and image quality variations. It includes multiple video tracks and complex cases similar to real-world environments.
dcterms:title: UFPR-ALPR dataset
